import React from 'react'
import Grid from '@material-ui/core/Grid'
import Paper from '@material-ui/core/Paper';

export default function Notes() {
  return (
    <Grid container spacing={1} xs={5}>
        <Grid item xs={5}>
          <Paper>xs=12</Paper>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={5}>
          <Paper>xs=6</Paper>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={1}>
          <Paper>xs=6</Paper>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={3}>
          <Paper>xs=3</Paper>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={3}>
          <Paper>xs=3</Paper>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={3}>
          <Paper>xs=3</Paper>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={3}>
          <Paper>xs=3</Paper>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    

  )
}
